race.description: Bet365 Same Race Multi Maiden Plate
race.comment: CONTOURS (13) is a two-start maiden who was a close-up fifth on debut then a solid fourth last time. Gets the extra ground now and the addition of blinkers. Expected to go close. BELLABAMA (10) has placed at all three this time in, the latest beaten less than a length over a mile. Overdue and will go close despite the draw. CHANTRA (7) was only a few lengths away fresh off a long break and will appreciate the extra ground. Fitter and should be in the finish. IMPACTICAL (4) was runner-up on debut then midfield last time. Looks suited by the extra ground now and has upside. PETE THE PROPHET (1) is another maiden who has started twice and is showing ability. Got home strongly to fifth latest and looks suited by the mile now.
